aces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcc200488ed64bb8b4d7cccab81aebaf447154ec","tid":450873,"uid":112709,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T16:51:29.000Z","msg":"你醒撚未，難聽啲講家陣你同送條女比人屌無分別，到時條女唔知輪流比幾多個中出你地就真係柒，你亦都最柒。唔好唔記得老蘭係咩地方﹐大把player可以喺條仔背後，令佢條女喺player什至一班人褲襠下喘息。<br />\n<br />\n我最後講多次，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你係男人就宜家飛的過去</span></span></strong>，搵個位坐低叫杯野最重要係睇實佢，你係暗地保護佢而唔係去玩，見到完場就即刻去接人，咪比人有機可乘。"},{"pid":"efe473eaebb4af1946aff43309098dfe873de0b2","tid":450873,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T16:59:58.000Z","msg":"識玩，乘機換畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}